<a href="artist.asp?id=9178">The Emerald Dawn</a> <span style="color:#777;font-size:9px;">Neo-Prog</span><br>

<p>Review by

<a href="Collaborators.asp?id=77068"><strong>Justanoldgit</strong></a>
</p>



<div style="color:#333;">


	<div class="avatarhp-box">
	<a href="https://www.progarchives.com/Collaborators.asp?id=77068">
	
	<img src="https://www.progarchives.com/forum/avatars/scenery_water_mountains.jpg" class="avatarhp" width=100 onerror="this.src='http://www.progarchives.com/forum/avatars/blank_avatar.jpg'" />
	</a>
