<img src="static-images/4stars.gif" alt="4 stars" border="0">
Just going to add to this and correct the change of rating back to its first value.  I do not know how or why this occurred.  The Emerald Dawn are a fine outfit who play interesting ORIGINAL music, and In Time is a great addition  to ANY collection.
The music is moody and sometimes sombre but always rewarding.
My remark to anyone in doubt is simply "Try it, you might like it!".
These musicians care deeply about their music and it shows.  I've been listening to music, both good and  bad for fifty years and I know quality when I hear it.  This is just such a thing. As time passed over the last few years I have noticed how hard it can be for such outfits to make their mark.  The Emerald Dawn  are one such outfit.</strong></strong></em></em>
</div>
</div>



